void '''PlayBounceSound''' (bool onFloor, double volume = 1.0)
== Usage == Plays the actors' {{property|BounceSound}} unless the actor has {{flag|NOBOUNCESOUND}}. If ''onFloor'' is false and the actor has {{flag|NOWALLBOUNCESND}}, then nothing plays. If the actors' {{property|BounceType}} is ''Doom/Heretic/HexenCompact'', then their {{property|SeeSound}} will always play in place of the dedicated bounce sounds. All sounds use the ''ATTN_IDLE'' attenuation (1.001).
== Parameters == *''onFloor'': Specifies if the bounce should be treated like a floor bounce. If not, then the actors' {{property|WallBounceSound}} is used, if any is defined. *''volume'': The volume with which the BounceSound players, from 0.0 to 1.0. {{git|27b6cb2}}
